neider/kqw.shtml" id="mwAns">"The History Of KQW Radio – KCBS"</a>. Bayarearadio.org<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwAnw">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwAn0">2009-07-22</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+History+Of+KQW+Radio+%E2%80%93+KCBS&amp;rft.pub=Bayarearadio.org&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bayarearadio.org%2Fschneider%2Fkqw.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARadio" class="Z3988" about="#mwt93" id="mwAn4"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt93" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwAn8"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-26" id="cite_note-26"><a href="./Radio#cite_ref-26" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-26" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt99" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite web ","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://jeff560.tripod.com/fm-max.html"},"title":{"wt":"The Most Powerful FM Stations"},"website":{"wt":"jeff560.tripod.com"},"access-date":{"wt":"2017-01-18"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAoA"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://jeff560.tripod.com/fm-max.html" id="mwAoE">"The Most Powerful FM Stations"</a>. <i id="mwAoI">jeff560.tripod.com</i><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwAoM">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwAoQ">2017-01-18</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=jeff560.tripod.com&amp;rft.atitle=The+Most+Powerful+FM+Stations&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fjeff560.tripod.com%2Ffm-max.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARadio" class="Z3988" 