Aqc">0-7453-0055-3</a><span about="#mwt124" id="mwAqg">, </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-7453-0055-9" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-7453-0055-9" about="#mwt124" id="mwAqk">978-0-7453-0055-9</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-33" id="cite_note-33"><a href="./Radio#cite_ref-33" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-33" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt127" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web ","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://www.pbs.org/tesla/ins/lab_remotec.html"},"title":{"wt":"Tesla – Master of Lightning: Remote Control"},"publisher":{"wt":"PBS"},"accessdate":{"wt":"2009-07-22"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAqo"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.pbs.org/tesla/ins/lab_remotec.html" id="mwAqs">"Tesla – Master of Lightning: Remote Control"</a>. PBS<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwAqw">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwAq0">2009-07-22</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Tesla+%E2%80%93+Master+of+Lightning%3A+Remote+Control&amp;rft.pub=PBS&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Ftesla%2Fins%2Flab_remotec.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARadio" class="Z3988" about="#mwt127" id="mwAq4"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt127" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwAq8"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-34" id="cite_note-34"><a href="./Radio#cite_ref-34" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-34" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt128" typeof="mw:Transclusio